<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>PNG, JPG PDF 변환</title>

    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/slider.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick-theme.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pdf-convert.css" />

    <style>
      /* footer {
	      position: relative;
	      margin-top: 80px;
      } */

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./nav') %>
    <%- include('./accordion') %>

    <main>
      <div id="uploadArea" class="upload-area" onclick="handleClick(event)" ondrop="handleDrop(event)" ondragover="handleDragOver(event)">
        <input type="file" class="upload" accept=".png, .jpg" id="fileInput" style="display: none" onchange="handleFileSelect()" multiple/>
        <div class="here">
          <img id="addImg" class="add-img" src="/images/folder-add.svg" />
          <p class="add-txt">클릭 또는 파일을 끌어다 놓으세요.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-container">
        <span>이미지 PDF 변환하기</span>
        <button class="upload-img-btn" type="button" onclick="handleClick(event)">이미지 업로드</button>
        <button class="convert-all-btn" type="button" onclick="convertAll()">모두 변환하기</button>
        <div class="open-help">
          <span>도움말(클릭)</span>
          <img class="help-icon" src="/images/help.svg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- <%- include('./slick') %> -->
      

    </div>
    <div class="help-modal">
      <div class="modal-overlay"></div>
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-content-wrapper">
          <img class="close-modal" src="/images/deletebtn.svg">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">사용방법</h1>
          <p>1. <b>"이미지 업로드"</b> 버튼을 클릭하여 변환하고자 하는 이미지를 업로드합니다.</p>
          <p>2. 또는 <b>좌측 영역을 클릭</b>하거나, <b>파일을 끌어다 놓아 줍니다.</b></p>
          <p>3. 업로드 영역에서 개별 이미지를 클릭해 pdf로 변환해 줍니다.</p>
          <p>4. 또는 <b>"모두 변환하기"</b>를 클릭해 업로드한 이미지 모두를 하나의 pdf로 변환합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./footer') %>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/slick.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/pdf-convert.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/common.js"></script>


  </body>
</html>
